WEBVTT

00:02.966 --> 00:04.200
Previously,
on "The Originals"...

00:04.201 --> 00:06.684
This town
was my home once,

00:06.685 --> 00:09.074
and in my absence,
Marcel has got

00:09.075 --> 00:10.656
everything
I ever wanted.

00:10.657 --> 00:12.285
I want it back.

00:12.286 --> 00:14.126
I hereby pledge
my allegiance to you.

00:14.127 --> 00:16.729
Celeste.
Celeste?

00:16.730 --> 00:19.063
Whoever she was,
she was smoking hot.

00:19.064 --> 00:20.431
I believe that when
you love someone,

00:20.432 --> 00:21.867
you're uniquely
vulnerable.

00:21.868 --> 00:23.169
She died because of me.

00:23.170 --> 00:24.870
Davina,
she's a powerful weapon.

00:24.871 --> 00:26.238
Yaah!

00:26.239 --> 00:27.540
I knew that I was supposed
to be killed

00:27.541 --> 00:30.509
so the harvest
could be completed.

00:30.510 --> 00:33.344
She is dead!
Do you hear me?

00:33.345 --> 00:35.936
4 were supposed
to rise, and none did.

00:35.937 --> 00:38.063
Where did
all that power go?

00:38.064 --> 00:41.186
Someone
called us forth. Who?

00:41.187 --> 00:42.721
I did.

00:42.722 --> 00:45.153
I'd appreciate if you
call me by my real name...

00:45.154 --> 00:47.225
Celeste.

00:51.230 --> 00:53.899
Oh...

00:53.900 --> 00:56.768
I remember
this cemetery.

00:56.769 --> 00:59.404
Hmm. Hasn't
changed a bit.

00:59.405 --> 01:01.545
I've been coming here
over a century

01:01.546 --> 01:03.879
wearing one face
or another.

