01:26.064 --> 01:30.101
Clara Summerlin,
will you come on?

01:30.102 --> 01:32.637
We're gonna miss
everything.

01:47.819 --> 01:49.634
Told you.

01:49.635 --> 01:51.720
Every witch in
the quarter is here,

01:51.721 --> 01:54.304
come to see the
great Papa Tunde.

02:15.513 --> 02:18.549
Witches of the french quarter,

02:18.550 --> 02:20.457
thank you for your welcome.

02:20.458 --> 02:22.584
It is good to be
among people of the faith.

02:22.585 --> 02:25.023
I, too, practice
ancestral magic,

02:25.024 --> 02:28.059
honoring those who walked
the path before us.

02:28.060 --> 02:30.674
From them we draw strength...

02:32.230 --> 02:34.221
And you will need strength,

02:34.222 --> 02:36.348
for a great darkness is coming.

02:36.349 --> 02:38.870
The city your forefathers
left you is now overrun

02:38.871 --> 02:41.977
by pirates, beasts,
and vampires.

02:59.830 --> 03:02.560
I practice
other magic, as well...

03:02.561 --> 03:04.000
Sacrificial magic.

03:04.001 --> 03:06.330
Channeling power
from the lives of my offerings,

03:06.331 --> 03:08.566
I use this strength
to vanquish my enemies,

03:08.567 --> 03:12.174
and I will punish your enemies
for their greed.

03:14.305 --> 03:18.841
In return, you will accept
my family into your coven...

03:21.779 --> 03:24.686
And me as your leader.

03:29.987 --> 03:33.190
Gentlemen,
make yourselves at home.

03:33.191 --> 03:35.333
Mayor O'Connell appears
to be running late,

03:35.334 --> 03:37.361
but there's much to discuss,
so I shall begin.

03:37.362 --> 03:39.896
One moment,
please, brother.

03:40.371 --> 03:41.999
You know
how much I enjoy

03:42.000 --> 03:44.267
these illicit,
little gatherings.

03:44.268 --> 03:45.836
Do not be troubled.

03:45.837 --> 03:47.738
Despite my brother's
reputation, I can assure you,

03:47.739 --> 03:49.421
we've invited you here
to broker in peace.

03:49.422 --> 03:50.974
You have my word.

03:50.975 --> 03:52.109
And, lucky for you,

03:52.110 --> 03:54.466
my brother always
keeps his word.

03:56.613 --> 04:00.583
You two are from
the guerrera crime family,

04:00.584 --> 04:03.654
a brutish pack
of thieves and killers,

04:03.655 --> 04:05.622
and that's nothing compared
to what you become

04:05.623 --> 04:07.124
on a full moon,
is it?

04:07.125 --> 04:08.258
Yes, yes, yes.

04:08.259 --> 04:09.860
Of course,
a bite from your kind

04:09.861 --> 04:11.461
is not lethal
to an original.

04:11.462 --> 04:13.630
Conflict between us
would not

04:13.631 --> 04:15.832
end well
for you at all.

04:15.833 --> 04:17.233
Let's state
our proposal here.

04:17.235 --> 04:19.451
My brother and I control
the ports of the city,

04:19.452 --> 04:21.471
but with prohibition
soon to be the law

04:21.471 --> 04:23.707
of the land, there'll be
a certain uptick

04:23.708 --> 04:27.310
in the kind of federal
presence we prefer to avoid.

04:27.311 --> 04:29.646
Therefore, I'd like
to suggest a system

04:29.647 --> 04:32.648
whereby... under our
supervision, of course...

04:32.649 --> 04:34.784
The guerrera family
can traffic alcohol

04:34.785 --> 04:36.920
into the city of
New Orleans for a profit.

04:36.921 --> 04:38.555
We would still be
in charge,

04:38.556 --> 04:42.125
but our rule would
remain a secret.

04:44.261 --> 04:46.162
This all
sounds very good,

04:46.163 --> 04:47.897
but, tell me,

04:47.898 --> 04:49.522
how will it benefit
the witches?

04:49.523 --> 04:51.633
I am sorry.
This is a private meeting.

04:52.151 --> 04:54.611
Yes, for kings
of the city,

04:54.612 --> 04:56.639
but I, too,
am a King,

04:56.640 --> 04:58.240
and I
have rules.

04:58.241 --> 05:01.143
I'm impressed.

05:01.577 --> 05:04.329
You're either quite ambitious
or quite mad.

05:04.330 --> 05:06.206
What's your name, mate?

05:06.207 --> 05:09.151
I am Alphonz
Bellatunde Delgallo,

05:09.585 --> 05:11.487
Papa Tunde
to my followers,

05:11.488 --> 05:12.922
and I come to ask
that the witches

05:12.923 --> 05:14.290
be granted
fair tribute

05:14.291 --> 05:16.339
for allowing your
existence in our city.

05:16.827 --> 05:18.628
Are you suggesting
that you speak

05:18.629 --> 05:20.595
for the french
quarter witches?

05:20.596 --> 05:22.764
I do now, and I expect

05:23.265 --> 05:25.868
our future negotiations
to go very smoothly.

05:25.869 --> 05:29.871
As a guarantee,
I brought a gift.

05:34.277 --> 05:37.485
I await our
next gathering.

05:52.061 --> 05:55.128
Well, I suppose
we'll need a new mayor.

05:57.415 --> 06:01.987
